      "writtenOn": "2026-02-26T01:51:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This has nothing to do with PLDM.\n\nIt\u0027s an entity-manager feature to be able to create associations between the inventory items that it holds.\n\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/entity-manager/blob/master/docs/associations.md\n\nIn this case i am creating `contained_by` association here to the chassis. If you look into the chassis config you will find a port with the same name.\n\nAt runtime this enables creating the correct associations between inventory items.",
