      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e lets figure out the right device.\n\n@ed@tanous.net @molberding@nvidia.com can you help with finding the information ?\n\nFrom what i can tell based on public information, i have no clue about this temp sensor. I can try different drivers but that only tells us what it isn\u0027t.\n\nAs written, yes the type of sensor is not entirely clear. But the driver works and the temperature reading is **real and useful**.\n\nSo i would consider the patch an improvement and if anyone knows it better they can always adjust this config 😊",
