      "message": "\u003e I assume that the temperature sensor is directly part of the SoC and not a separate chip.\n\nExactly, so a TMP421 device in your EM config isn\u0027t appropriate here unless you actually have a TMP421.  If you want to invent a new device called \"connectx6 temp sensor\" that\u0027s fine, but please don\u0027t put in configs that we know to be incorrect.",
